    "The diversity of opinion depends of the recommender system, pointing to another harmful consequences for online sanity.",
    "Indeed, while Chrono and Neg lead to the same σ inter/intra op, the two social modes, namely Pop & PopNeg, result into a higher fragmentation of the social fabric.",
